## mongos.conf, this file is enforced by puppet.

## where to write logging data.
systemLog:
  verbosity: <%= @verbosity %>
  destination: <%= @destination %>
  logAppend: <%= @logAppend %>
  path: <%= @systemLogPath %>

## network interfaces
net:
  port: <%= @port %>
  bindIp: <%= @bindIp %>

## sharding
sharding:
  configDB: <%= @configDB %>